    dc:description "Fig. 37. Size frequency histograms of head capsule width for Soyedina calcarea from the Kentucky type locality. A: May 2002 – April 2003; B: May 2003 – April 2004. Numbers on top give number of specimens per month; n = 2300 nymphs total across the two‐year sampling period. Vertical arrows refer to adult flight period." ;
